\begin{frame}{Summary}
\begin{itemize}
\item EVS stands for Environmental Studies.
\item EVS aims to inculcate the concern for environment in  learners. 
\item Children learn EVS through community, teacher, parents, and textbooks.
\item EVS textbooks should be designed to evoke curiousity and provide opportunities for the child to explore. 
\end{itemize}
